data.description: If you're looking for a comfortable, cozy home in a great school district on the outskirts of Lafayette, you just found it! This 3 bed, 2 bath home features a wide open floor plan with a spacious feel in each room! Tray ceilings and crown molding give this home a style that you won't find in today's new homes! Outside you'll enjoy a large 14x30 RV cover, perfect for storing your camper or boat! Whether you're a first time home buyer or someone looking for the perfect location, this home has it all! Be sure to schedule your showing today while it's still available!
